9B%E9%98%B4%E9%AA%98%E6%96%87/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E6%96%87%E6%98%8C%E5%B8%9D%E5%90%9B%E9%98%B4%E9%AA%98%E6%96%87/</guid><description>帝君曰：吾(帝)一十七世为士大夫身。未尝虐民酷吏。救人之难，济人之急，悯人之孤，容人之过。广行阴骘[yīn zhì]，上格苍穹。人能如我(帝)</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>文昌帝君阴骘文</category><category>早晚课</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category></item></channel></rss>